Events.PluginDescription: Track Events and get reports on your visitors activity.
Events.AvgValueDocumentation: The average of all values for this event
Events.EventActionsReportDocumentation: This report shows you the actions that were tracked for any event. You can view the event categories and names that were tracked along with an event action in each rows subtable
Events.EventCategoriesReportDocumentation: This report shows you the categories that were tracked for any event. You can view the event actions and names that were tracked along with an event category in each rows subtable
Events.EventNamesReportDocumentation: This report shows you the names that were tracked for any event. You can view the event actions and categories that were tracked along with an event name in each rows subtable
Events.EventsWithValueDocumentation: Number of events where an Event value was set
Events.EventValueTooltip: Total Event value is the sum of %1$s events values %2$s between minimum of %3$s and maximum of %4$s.
Events.MaxValueDocumentation: The maximum value for this event
Events.MinValueDocumentation: The minimum value for this event
